g src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/03/143128_51dfdba9053b0a7b37666192c9d2e48a.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F03%2F143128_51dfdba9053b0a7b37666192c9d2e48a.png&h=eedafbdd&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/03/143134_7d42b187741e40b466ed36acf5b41640.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F03%2F143134_7d42b187741e40b466ed36acf5b41640.png&h=cda66df7&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/03/143144_b1af6c621466fbf36f10eec78c8ce9fd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F03%2F143144_b1af6c621466fbf36f10eec78c8ce9fd.png&h=4346cee7&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/03/143608_50d56b4ee3e2156c99a81a57f3edf343.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F03%2F143608_50d56b4ee3e2156c99a81a57f3edf343.png&h=4b4951a7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我地2個雞啄唔斷咁差唔多食左成2個鐘<br />\n不斷講西藏有幾辛苦 點捱苦法"},{"pid":"f2388addcdccb1292f39ec771d9e413a5f1449ab","tid":685920,"uid":81026,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T07:09:32.000Z","msg":"食到飽飽之後<br />\n諗住係附近搵間平既旅館休息下<br />\n但間間都話唔受我張回鄉証<br />\n話入唔到個登記系統<br />\n搞到冇得係呢個平區到住<br />\n跟住杭州妹就揸佢架bmw x1黎接我返出去市區<br />\n我當時心諗 人仔細細居然揸部咁大架車<br />\n我都唔係好大心信心，<br />\n但一上佢車後即刻改觀晒，佢手車快狠準<br />\n佢問左幾個朋友後<br />\n幫我搵到間大酒店先可以比我呢個外賓入住<br />\n成日話香港係中國既一部分 但我揸住張回鄉証成日都搵唔到地方住 麻鬼煩 西藏又係咁 杭州又係咁 都唔知上海會唔會又係咁<br />\n大酒店要成210蚊一晚<br />\n但環境的確唔錯<br />\n可以訓返教好既<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/03/150845_67b46271c99691617976956f0545fb8b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F03%2F150845_67b46271c99691617976956f0545fb8b.png&h=b4f94442&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/03/150851_d6695e6ff3b345f67ebd35a45c1f526e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F03%2F150851_d6695e6ff3b345f67ebd35a45c1f526e.png&h=225a4c08&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/03/150856_5be67110342741d3b46a7ba2f187ee38.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F03%2F150856_5be67110342741d3b46a7ba2f187ee38.png&h=0b9bf6f9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/03/150905_934d1ee73bb2e3537e70f56df4ea2df1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F03%2F150905_934d1ee73bb2e3537e70f56df4ea2df1.png&h=16cbfcd4&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/03/150910_35f5f916334b2dd24a457509431b1402.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F03%2F150910_35f5f916334b2dd24a457509431b1402.png&h=7538b1f2&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/03/150916_f570d1311f88c6c9e40e85d8ff0bfd74.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F03%2F150916_f570d1311f88c6c9e40e85d8ff0bfd74.png&h=6abfa740&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/03/150922_2647a1ba51fc6ae143b5fcca2482f70b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F03%2F150922_2647a1ba51fc6ae143b5fcca2482f70b.png&h=bebe65bc&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/03/150929_cec140b3eace778ae0ebf3f40d75e6f4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F03%2F150929_cec140b3eace778ae0ebf3f40d75e6f4.png&h=8a25a5f7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7d95c1461f74a0203c5865eec9791810ab4b1d68","tid":685920,"uid":81026,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T07:38:48.000Z","msg":"第2朝8點鐘個鬧鐘就響起了<br />\n真係好唔想起身<br />\n張床實在太舒服<br />\n刷牙洗臉差唔多到9點<br />\n杭州妹就到左酒店大堂等我<br />\n跟住我地一齊去佢間舞蹈室附近食早餐<br />\n呢到完全冇任何游遊客類似當地街市咁<br />\n仲見到一大班大媽跳舞 慶祝開張<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/03/153819_3560d0ca85fce62d726708e5fabcdebc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F03%2F153819_3560d0ca85fce62d726708e5fabcdebc.png&h=26d00e13&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/03/153824_20d9443145090ca5189988e8ad480538.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F03%2F153824_20d9443145090ca5189988e8ad480538.png&h=c1c91d49&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"768b78c5d7196ff149623b1bd572305d1775b041","tid":685920,"uid":81026,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T07:59:16.000Z","msg":"入左間鋪頭叫野食<br />\n呢間野真係好有特色<br />\n好有當地風味<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/03/155053_94f00cfcba6e5f78235589fd200c3ab0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F03%2F155053_94f00cfcba6e5f78235589fd200c3ab0.png&h=233898d5&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/03/155102_fcaef6cc080264b32ddb0c08369ad615.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F03%2F155102_fcaef6cc080264b32ddb0c08369ad615.png&h=7e86a796&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/03/155107_843ade9f5b3bcb27b5cd13113f9f5383.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F03%2F155107_843ade9f5b3bcb27b5cd13113f9f5383.png&h=c4e22b47&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/03/155112_6377b94c03a56b8f4b5e0096f57a4539.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F03%2F155112_6377b94c03a56b8f4b5e0096f57a4539.png&h=6e9f4fb0&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/03/155912_4a26bf3317708286721da1089f691c70.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F03%2F155912_4a26bf3317708286721da1089f691c70.png&h=3c293589&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n之後叫左抄面，竹筍雲吞，一個唔知乜野大餅，仲有一個當地特色鹹豆漿，呢到先17蚊 勁底<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/03/155446_fb44d1945372c6cd69475e50a1b9d9f9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F03%2F155446_fb44d1945372c6cd69475e50a1b9d9f9.png&h=a654024d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n食緊野時發現左一個細佬係到執碗 應該得9歲左右 唔洗返學就係到幫手 真係好乖<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/03/155754_3a3ae035dfd720ecb3a8a4367ee2a413.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F03%2F155754_3a3ae035dfd720ecb3a8a4367ee2a413.png&h=1dfdf950&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/03/155805_f194fabd2f43f3d9567343f9cacb17cb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F03%2F155805_f194fabd2f43f3d9567343f9cacb17cb.png&h=f53fb6b8&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/03/155818_48ce87cff2a870b240b2cb5932115c1d.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F03%2F155818_48ce87cff2a870b240b2cb5932115c1d.png&h=ca22def4&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/03/155834_090611eeb40c3c8a60b31649fc3d0527.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F03%2F155834_090611eeb40c3c8a60b31649fc3d0527.png&h=dd1e71bf&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"86ceafb50e35f52803510cb88c56e2f929cb2a5c","tid":685920,"uid":81026,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T09:25:44.000Z","msg":"之後我地兩個就揸車去青山湖到玩<br />\n其實我都唔清楚呢到有乜好玩 人地帶就黎玩<br />\n一路上都修路 要兜個圈先去到<br />\n去到原來係行步道 可以望到成個湖<br />\n加上今日係星期六 好多一家大細黎玩<br />\n杭州妹問踩單車好唔好<br />\n我緊係話好 唔洗行又可以影到相 何樂而不為<br />\n沿途仲一路介紹我識不同既樹同花<br />\n仲比我地見到心形既繡球花<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/03/172222_e4e444d6556d0cd282c5b2b8b023821d.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F03%2F172222_e4e444d6556d0cd282c5b2b8b023821d.png&h=fe46c15f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/03/172227_d6985b441efe625d65c0e49fe1efd002.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F03%2F172227_d6985b441efe625d65c0e49fe1efd002.png&h=3e61f784&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/03/172231_5899fc9a4600fcea67e365e686ccfba7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F03%2F172231_5899fc9a4600fcea67e365e686ccfba7.png&h=076d17fc&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/03/172235_f5549ba372976005ee61ef4eef5127ac.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F03%2F172235_f5549ba372976005ee61ef4eef5127ac.png&h=71432368&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/03/172240_0123e7a529a90c7c63074716e04798bb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F03%2F172240_0123e7a529a90c7c63074716e04798bb.png&h=6d622383&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/03/172259_c5ae9ffde2be26a41f138ed41266ad45.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupl